Package API.Fractal

Contains the logic for storing the user's password files. The logic for encrypting, decrypting and deleting the decrypted copy of the user's password file.
Contains Fractal Encryption, Fractal Decryption.
This adheres to the Fractal File Saving System Specification 4 which is the strongest ever in this iteration of program security.

NOTE:
You can check out the developer documentation for Fractal File Saving System here.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FractalInterface
    Encrypts, Decrypts and deletes the decrypted Fractal Files.
